{"TopicId":209648,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"Kerbal Ball","CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-06T09:35:46Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-06T09:35:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLicense: CC-BY-SA-4.0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLink: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://spacedock.info/mod/3111/Kerbal%20Ball\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://spacedock.info/mod/3111/Kerbal Ball\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:24px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EIf you control your craft using a keyboard then just make sure your pitch control isn\u0027t the same key as your rover acceleration control.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi. Kerbals take the health of their team very seriously, so much so that they will put them in protective bubbles.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is the Kerbal Ball, a 2 piece vehicle for a single kerbal to get around. Very simple for a bit of fun.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe outer piece is the wheel and like all wheels once attached it needs to be rotated clockwise 90 degrees to work out in the world.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a good one to have the internal overlay on all the time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe pod has 4 extra nodes, front, back, up and down so it can be used for other things but it cannot be surface attached. There are no internal props. It is the right way up when spawned in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nType hampster or ball in parts for them to pop up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEnjoy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Kerbal_Ball-1662456655.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002264.00\u0022 height=\u0022677\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://spacedock.info/content/ColdJ_60612/Kerbal_Ball/Kerbal_Ball-1662456655.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022hLUdnYK.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002264.00\u0022 height=\u0022677\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/hLUdnYK.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-09-09T01:26:19Z\u0022 title=\u002209/09/2022 01:26  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 9, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by ColdJ\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"darthvader15001","CreatedById":222173,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-06T10:53:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFirst\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E seriously, good mod!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nedit: this is my 200th post!!\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-09-06T23:14:56Z\u0022 title=\u002209/06/2022 11:14  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 6, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by darthvader15001\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EYay\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Space Scumbag","CreatedById":70411,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-06T12:05:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHahaha, no wayyy\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"darthvader15001","CreatedById":222173,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-06T23:13:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm I have to put this on a rocket and make it renter and hit the ground at 650m/s\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-07T04:12:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224172086\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209648\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221662506038\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022222173\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022darthvader15001\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, darthvader15001 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm I have to put this on a rocket and make it renter and hit the ground at 650m/s\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMeanie.\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tajwo","CreatedById":222600,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-07T14:17:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI remember playing a PC game when I was younger, about a hamster in a ball rattling around obstacle courses....\u003Cstrong\u003EAha, I have the perfect idea!\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"flart","CreatedById":181486,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-08T19:50:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncould you put an arrow pointing up on the wheel, to make clear how it need to be placed?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-09T00:58:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224171739\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209648\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221662456946\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211123\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ColdJ\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/6/2022 at 7:35 PM, ColdJ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe outer piece is the wheel and like all wheels once attached it needs to be rotated clockwise 90 degrees to work out in the world.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/181486-flart/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022181486\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/181486-flart/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@flart\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi. I know that when you have only dealt with wheels that have shock towers that it can be confusing at first. All wheels from everywhere (except for a confusing one from Fast corp where the node was backwards) enter the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E with the top pointing out the open doors and seeing as a wheel needs to have it\u0027s top pointing up when on a rover in order to work, they need to be rotated 90 degrees clockwise to work. So If you spawn the ball cockpit into the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E first and don\u0027t change anything then grab the outer ball wheel and click it to it\u0027s node, again without changing any orientation. Once on click on the rotation tool then click on the ball wheel you will see that the blue line is horizontal and the red line vertical. Use the rotation tool to turn it clockwise till the blue line is now vertical and it is ready to go out into the world.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rutabaga22","CreatedById":221143,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-09T01:01:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould I stack them side to side? Also, is there CTT support?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-09T01:05:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224172923\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209648\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221662685307\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221143\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rutabaga22\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Rutabaga22 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould I stack them side to side? Also, is there CTT support?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnly if you build a frame work off the cockpit balls extra nodes as 2 wheels by themselves would not be controlable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat is CTT?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rutabaga22","CreatedById":221143,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-09T01:06:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224172927\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209648\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221662685540\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211123\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ColdJ\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, ColdJ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCTT\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCommunity tech tree\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-09T01:10:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224172928\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209648\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221662685578\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221143\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rutabaga22\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Rutabaga22 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCommunity tech tree\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI haven\u0027t done anything to them other than stock and I have made them available right from the Start. If you whant to make them something to have to work for then you will need to edit your config files or create a \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Module Manager (mod)\u0022\u003EMM\u003C/abbr\u003E patch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rutabaga22","CreatedById":221143,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-09T01:15:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI tried it and it just kinda spun me around.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-09T01:19:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224172934\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209648\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221662686100\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221143\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rutabaga22\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Rutabaga22 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI tried it and it just kinda spun me around.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou tried what?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe outer is a wheel. Just at a guess, you wouldn\u0027t have your pitch control still on the same key as your rover acceleration control would you?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rutabaga22","CreatedById":221143,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-09T01:20:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224172937\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209648\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221662686349\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211123\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ColdJ\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, ColdJ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\npitch control still on the same key as your rover acceleration control would you?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do... why?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-09T01:22:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224172938\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209648\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221662686402\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221143\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rutabaga22\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Rutabaga22 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do... why?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is a cockpit inside a wheel with nothing to stop it turning over other than a reaction wheel. You hit the pitch control and you are tumbling the cockpit over, so you just need to assign one or the other to a different key.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fletch4","CreatedById":209690,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-09T01:31:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmy brother was playing *eugh* fortnite when i saw this, and i got flashbacks...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"flart","CreatedById":181486,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-09T10:03:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224172922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209648\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221662685120\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211123\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ColdJ\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/9/2022 at 3:58 AM, ColdJ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n90 degrees clockwise\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was able to make it work because of this line in the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, but it is much easier to just have arrow as in the Kerbal Foundries, and note in the description of the part, to make sure the arrow points up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-09-12T07:25:20Z\u0022 title=\u002209/12/2022 07:25  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 12, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by flart\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JadeOfMaar","CreatedById":167617,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-09T18:43:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Bubble_Boy_movie_poster.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022147.88\u0022 height=\u0022383\u0022 width=\u0022259\u0022 src=\u0022https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/73/Bubble_Boy_movie_poster.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nChange my mind.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tajwo","CreatedById":222600,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-10T16:55:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGet back here!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00228Mshe43.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002284.67\u0022 height=\u0022725\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/8Mshe43.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zer0Kerbal","CreatedById":190933,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-12T05:03:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003Ethe look on that kerbals face: priceless!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"flart","CreatedById":181486,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-24T17:04:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it possible to board the Kerbal Ball in-flight ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso I have problem to build a vehicle in the construction mode. I have made a patch for volume, but default orientation is probably different, transparent arrows would help with the orientation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode\u0022\u003E@PART[CJHampsterPod]\n{\n\t@category = Utility\n\t@title = Kerbal Ball Protection (Inner)\n\t\n\t-MODULE[ModuleInventoryPart]{}\n\t\n    MODULE\n    {\n        name = ModuleCargoPart\n        packedVolume = 520   // d = 1m, v = 523 \n    }\n}\n\n@PART[CJHampsterWheel]\n{\t\n\t@category = Utility\n\t@title = Kerbal Ball Motive (Outer)\n\t@description ^= :^:\u0026lt;i\u0026gt;Use rotation tool on the ball wheel. You will see, that the blue line is horizontal and the red line vertical. Turn it clockwise till the blue line is  vertical and it is ready to go out into the world.\u0026lt;/i\u0026gt;\\n\\n: \n\t\n    MODULE\n    {\n        name = ModuleCargoPart\n        packedVolume = 1770  // d = 1.5, v = 1767\n    }\n}\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-25T02:51:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224178533\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209648\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221664039049\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181486\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022flart\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, flart said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it possible to board the Kerbal Ball in-flight ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is completely up to your skill level. It has an airlock but not a ladder to grab as it is a ball and if you were on a ladder you would be flung all over the place.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis was never designed to be put together in EVA construction.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis was a one off mod to just have a bit of fun. I will not be altering it or updating it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBased on it\u0027s size I wouldn\u0027t think it would be able to be put in an inventory slot. If you want it to be able to be used in EVA construction then you are probably better off with.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 MODULE\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0{\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0name = ModuleCargoPart\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0stackableQuantity = 1\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0packedVolume = -1\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0}\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe rotation tool in EVA probably has the same orientation as when in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E or the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E, never taken the time to check,so that could be used to work out which way up. I do know that in EVA the part is always brought out of inventory the same way up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI make all my mods freely open to be played around with by whoever downloads them so if you wish to change them for Your OWN Game then that is fine. If you want any physical changes to the model then I suggest you read my thread on using the .mu plugin with Blender/BforArtists 3 and adjust the model to your liking. Everything you need is free to download and I have given info on a lot of aspects. All you will probably need to do is pick a section you want as different and change it\u0027s position on the UV map to be over that colour. Just remember that .dds are upside down compared to everything else and so you might want to make a flipped version that is saved as a PNG and rename the original to something else as you work so that it looks right in the 3d program.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere is the link.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022211123\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1181555400\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/206781-somewhere-to-put-any-knowledge-learned-about-using-the-mu-plugin/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=4087557\u0026amp;embedComment=4087557\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022 style=\u0022height:296px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood Luck.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tajwo","CreatedById":222600,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-10T15:34:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224172086\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209648\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221662506038\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022222173\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022darthvader15001\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/7/2022 at 2:13 AM, darthvader15001 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm I have to put this on a rocket\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks like someone already did that \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI completely forgot I had this mod installed and had one of these spawn in while doing a rescue contract (it told me to recover the craft too, so that\u0027s why the spacecraft has a klaw). I thought it was one of the pods from Making History at first.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022TaToDc8.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002284.67\u0022 height=\u0022725\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/TaToDc8.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI forgot reaction wheels and batteries so I did this mission with the OKTO2\u0027s internal battery (5 EC) and relying on the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E to maneuver. I packed a lot of monoprop so it didn\u0027t end in disaster...yet. I had to hibernate the OTKO2 a few times to save EC. i forgot parachutes too\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHopefully the ball can survive Kerbin re-entry from returning from the M\u00FCn.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t worry she still survived.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-10-10T15:43:23Z\u0022 title=\u002210/10/2022 03:43  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 10, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by tajwo\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbal123_Furry","CreatedById":222628,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-13T08:17:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat\u0027s this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJebster ball?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKamster ball??\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}